org.afplib.afplib.impl

Class FontDescriptorSpecificationImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.BasicNotifierImpl
      • org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.BasicEObjectImpl
        • org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FontDescriptorSpecification, Triplet, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class FontDescriptorSpecificationImpl
extends TripletImpl
implements FontDescriptorSpecification
    An implementation of the model object 'Font Descriptor Specification'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Ft Wt Class
    • Ft Wd Class
    • Ft Height
    • Ft Width
    • Ft Ds Flags
    • Ft Us Flags
